comments: Covington (PHI) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot, making "high-five" contact after the ball is released.

call_type: Turnover:  Out of Bounds - Bad Pass Turn
comments: Embiid's (PHI) pass goes out of bounds without touching an opponent.
During the dribble hand-off, White (BOS) releases the pass and turns to screen Embiid (PHI) with his backside. The contact that occurs is marginal.
Maxey (PHI) avoids making contact with Porzingis's (BOS) arm during his jump shot attempt.
Porzingis (BOS) moves laterally into Maxey (PHI) and initiates body contact that affects his SQBR.
Melton's (PHI) jump shot attempt goes out of bounds.
Maxey (PHI) reaches in and initiates contact across White's (BOS) left arm, affecting his SQBR.
Holiday (BOS) is in a legal guarding position when incidental contact occurs with Melton (PHI) during his drive.  Melton loses his balance on his own, and not as a result of any illegal contact.
Maxey (PHI) brings his arms forward and marginal contact occurs with Tatum's (BOS) front during his driving shot attempt.
Batum (PHI) releases the throw-in within five seconds.
Tatum (BOS) reaches in and makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Embiid (PHI) posting up.
Maxey (PHI) legally contests Brown's (BOS) jump shot attempt.
Brown (BOS) cleanly blocks Maxey's (PHI) jump shot attempt.
Maxey's (PHI) shot attempt does not hit the rim and the shot clock expires thereafter.
Beverley (PHI) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Porzingis' (BOS) arm.
White (BOS) briefly gets his hand on the ball as Embiid (PHI) secures the rebound and any ensuing contact is incidental.
After securing the rebound, Embiid (PHI) steps out of bounds with his right foot while still in possession of the ball.
